  <brief_title>Resistance Training as Treatment of Achilles Tendinopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Heavy Slow Resistance Versus Eccentric Training in the Treatment of Achilles Tendinopathy. A Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
